### Blur an image

```sass

// Add a background image
body {
    background: url("../public/img/project-2.jpg") no-repeat center center/cover;
    height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
}
```


```sass
 // Add Layer and use blur effect
#modal-container {
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 1;
    /*  Add Background blur*/
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0, 0.2);
}
```
